channel.title: How to I change so that it takes the characters passwords not random keys
channel.description: How to I change so that it takes the characters passwords not random keys, is it like a anti-password or something that makes it put it on a ramdom number and letter code? For example I log on server with password as 12345 and it says in characters that my password is 48626de25144dfceb320a0f04f3a9d30. Can someone tell me how to make it so it says the password 12345 instead of random numbers and letters?
